        <hr/>
                        
<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Akiva Goldsman was born on July 7, 1962 in New York City, New York, USA. He is a producer and writer, known for <a href="/title/tt0480249?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">I Am Legend</a> (2007), <a href="/title/tt0268978?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">A Beautiful Mind</a> (2001) and <a href="/title/tt0343818?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">I, Robot</a> (2004).            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0326040/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
        <h4 class="inline">Born:</h4> 
   
  <time datetime="1962-7-7" itemprop="birthDate">
<a href="/search/name?birth_monthday=7-7&refine=birth_monthday&ref_=nm_ov_bth_monthday"
>July 7</a>, 
     
<a href="/search/name?birth_year=1962&ref_=nm_ov_bth_year"
>1962</a>    
  </time>
            in
            <a href="/search/name?birth_place=New+York+City,+New+York,+USA&ref_=nm_ov_bth_place"
>New York City, New York, USA</a>
    </div>

                        
                        
