                <h4 class="inline">Personal Quote:</h4>
The more you work with someone, the better you work together. There is nothing more difficult than learning to work with another person. And nothing more gratifying. So why would you want to abandon that? [on constantly working with <a href="/name/nm0000165?ref_=nm_dyk_qt1">Ron Howard</a> and <a href="/name/nm0000128?ref_=nm_dyk_qt2">Russell Crowe</a>]                    <span class="see-more inline">
